title: 02 - When 500 People Get Saved at a Rave with Luke Lefevre and Daniel MacLeod
description:
This is one of those stories you won't believe! Meet my friends Luke and Daniel. They live risky, bold lives with Jesus and have seen God move in people's lives as a result. Listen all the way to the end. Don't miss this episode and share it with a friend!
